### **Final Results:**
- âœ… Files created in `outputs/models/`
- âœ… HTML files created in `outputs/visualizations/`
- âœ… Topics make clinical sense (medical terms)
- âœ… Interactive visualizations open in browser

### **Performance Benchmarks:**
- **Good coherence:** > 0.4
- **Great coherence:** > 0.5  
- **Processing speed:** ~1000 docs/minute
- **Training time:** 5-15 minutes for 5K docs

